the full spectrum of our clients financing needs as a patient longterm investor with permanent capital we have developed a reputation for the flexibility of our approach a willingness to hold large positions and the ability to offer sponsors and management teams increased certainty of execution we provide flexible debt capital to middlemarket companies and on a lesser scale to i power generation projects and ii early stage and emerging growth companies backed by venture capital firms    we have elected to be regulated as a business development company bdc under the investment company act of  and the rules and regulations promulgated thereunder our common stock is publicly traded on the nasdaq global select market under the ticker symbol arcc ares capital is the largest bdc by both market capitalization and total assets with approximately  billion of total assets as of march   on january   ares capital closed its acquisition of american capital ltd nasdaq acas enhancing arccs position as a leading direct lender to us middle market companies the partners and investment committee members for ares capitals investment adviser possess an average of more than  years of relevant experience   ares capital is externally managed by ares capital management llc ares capital management a subsidiary of ares management lp nyseares ares a publicly traded leading global alternative asset manager with offices located across the us europe and asia ares capital management is able to leverage the power of the broader ares platform to access resources relationships and significant capital markets trading and research expertise to provide arcc with attractive investment opportunities   ares capitals portfolio company ivy hill asset management lp iham an sec registered investment adviser manages  vehicles and serves as the submanager or subservicer for two other vehicles as of march   in conjuction with the completion of the acquisition on january   american capital asset management llc aca